{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The alternative was probably much worse if I didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was easy for me to do that because my movements in the factory itself were a guarantee that I could almost go anyplace because I had to walk to offices.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, at one time, I was in charge also of maintaining fires when we were building Schindler's offices.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was during the winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were barrels of fire, and I had to keep feeding them with wood so it would keep the concrete work and the brick work somewhat warm as-- as they were building the offices.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes in the middle of 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the war was turning bad against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russians were advancing westwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Schindler was ordered to deliver 700 of the people that he had-- of the 1,000 people that he had there, he was ordered to deliver back to Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this would have been in the summer of 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, I remember standing in formation where Oskar Schindler, together with SS guards and dogs by their sides, were walking up and down the-- the rows of the 1,000 workforce and selecting people that would remain in-- evidently now I know, but at that time I didn't know which group is meant for what.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I remember them doing the selecting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at one point in time, I realized-- or at least it occurred to me, right or wrong-- it occurred to me that maybe I am in the wrong group of people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when Schindler came close to where I was standing in that formation, with the SS guards being there, I stepped out of the formation, stepped up to Oskar Schindler, and yelled out to Oskar Schindler, Herr Schindler, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
